# AndroidForClaw

Android AI Agent Runtime - Give AI the ability to use Android phones.

## Tech Stack
- Kotlin + Java, MVVM + Repository
- OpenAI-compatible API (Claude Opus 4.6)
- Floating Window, AccessibilityService
- ADB JNI, QuickJS JavaScript Runtime

## Key Modules
- **Agent**: AgentLoop, Skills System, Tools
- **UI**: Floating Window, Chat Interface
- **Gateway**: Feishu, Discord (Multi-channel)
- **Extensions**: BrowserForClaw, Self-Control

## Constraints
- Complete modifications and end directly, no summaries
- Don't run tests automatically, only when requested 